Every parent knows that at some stage their child will tell a white lie or two as justification for not doing well in a test or exam. If you happen to be a parent with presidential ambitions, it is absolutely important that you take what your kids, grandchildren, or those of your friends say with a pinch of salt. Dlamini-Zuma has made a mampara of herself by claiming that former whites-only public schools teach anti-ANC propaganda. As for her claims about Wits, maybe her daughter Thuthukile, who studied anthropology at the institution, needs to do some explaining.